{"id":286448,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-成都温江失地农民曾少梅上访被拘留期满/","date":"2013-03-28T07:16:15Z","modified":"2013-03-28T07:16:15Z","title":"维权网 | 成都温江失地农民曾少梅上访被拘留期满，成都维权人士前往迎接并举牌抗议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员琳娜报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点</span><span>左右，因上访被温江当局以“扰乱社会秩序”拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日的温江实地农民曾少梅，拘留期满走出了拘留所，成都维权人士陈云飞、李廷惠、王蓉文等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>余人前往迎接英雄的曾少梅。</span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">         </span></div>\n<div><span>接出曾少梅后，这二十多名维权人士，一起来到非法拘留曾少梅的寿安镇派出所，并举标语“迫害妇女是孬种”以示抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">         </span></div>\n<div><span>一起聚餐后，他们又打出“中国梦不是噩梦”，表达对法制中国的期待。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">         </span></div>\n<div><span>曾少梅是因为被非法强征后，多年没有获得合理赔偿，向各级部门反映均相互推诿，才去北京上访，被截访回来后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>在大街上被绑架，然后送去行政拘留的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">         </span></div>\n<div><span>据了解：成都维稳十分疯狂，因上访回来被拘留的人数不胜数，她们均是被编造理由进行行政处罚，她们向法院起诉，法院同样包庇公安的违法行为，没有一例起诉后能够胜诉的，但成都访民还是继续坚持起诉，她们希望法制中国的梦想，通过她们的努力，不再是维权人的噩梦。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">         </span></div>\n<div><span>采访电话：曾少梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13348809075</span><span>，陈云飞：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13980888964</span><span>，王蓉文：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13608062557,</span><span>李廷惠</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13980428916</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qfbOq1sGYsA/UVO5swZ32bI/AAAAAAAAfZI/3ib0EAYe6l8/s1600/%E6%9B%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A2%85%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qfbOq1sGYsA/UVO5swZ32bI/AAAAAAAAfZI/3ib0EAYe6l8/s320/%E6%9B%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A2%85%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BV187w01iFs/UVO5uq0-PGI/AAAAAAAAfZQ/V4iqOJJ2s2o/s1600/%E4%BC%A0%E5%94%A4%E8%AF%81.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BV187w01iFs/UVO5uq0-PGI/AAAAAAAAfZQ/V4iqOJJ2s2o/s320/%E4%BC%A0%E5%94%A4%E8%AF%81.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Nw7KXPz79CQ/UVO5w2_TXQI/AAAAAAAAfZY/DE1Zfz9fOIA/s1600/%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Nw7KXPz79CQ/UVO5w2_TXQI/AAAAAAAAfZY/DE1Zfz9fOIA/s320/%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Q5E-GuBW2Ak/UVO5yg_nQYI/AAAAAAAAfZg/OnUkRmceeT4/s1600/%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%89%80%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Q5E-GuBW2Ak/UVO5yg_nQYI/AAAAAAAAfZg/OnUkRmceeT4/s320/%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%89%80%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IWUtM_XzSHI/UVO522pDU_I/AAAAAAAAfZo/lhkXlqXWik0/s1600/%E4%B8%89%E8%AF%81.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IWUtM_XzSHI/UVO522pDU_I/AAAAAAAAfZo/lhkXlqXWik0/s320/%E4%B8%89%E8%AF%81.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-tr7kM8J6wI0/UVO54Yimq6I/AAAAAAAAfZw/p4jbo3jLM_8/s1600/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A2%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%99%A9%E6%